title: Park Confirms Respiratory Disease Outbreak in Bighorn Sheep (NPS - National Park Service)
text: ( Source : NPS - National Park Service ) A yearling bighorn lamb showing symptoms of disease. Note the crusty discharge around the nostrils and overall thin appearance. NPS/ Michael Vamstad News Release Date : October 8, 2015 Contact : George
